Image Sharing

Ephemeral way to share your pictures

using:
NodeJs
ExpressJs
SocketIO

WIP - help us on our chat
[![Gitter](https://badges.gitter.im/Join%20Chat.svg)](https://gitter.im/TwanoO67/image-sharing?utm_source=badge&utm_medium=badge&utm_campaign=pr-badge)

